subproject.description: This project supports a Diagnostic Trade Integrated Study to produce a framework for trade policy development in Tuvalu.  It is the catalyst for further work to mainstream trade for sustainable human development and poverty reduction into national plans and strategies.
subproject.title: Tuvalu Diagnotic Trade Study
